**"Adding Dynamic Routing to Static Sites: Performance and Flexibility"**

Because GitHub Pages uses a **pure static hosting model with no server-side logic**, any multilingual handling had to rely entirely on client-side scripts.

This project migrated to **Cloudflare Pages**, keeping the speed of **SSG (Static Site Generation)** while adopting a **hybrid approach** that detects language at request time through **Edge Functions (middleware)**.

